      • standardPositionControllerRequest

        protected void standardPositionControllerRequest(int jointID,
                                                 boolean isStandardPositionControllerRequested)
                                          throws MasteringException
        Sets the request for the standard position controller. All mastering motions used for the detection of the mastering notch must be performed with the standard position controller.
        Parameters:
        jointID - joint ID
        isStandardPositionControllerRequested - flag signaling the request of the standard position controller; true : standard position controller, false : configured controller
        Throws:
        MasteringException - if the request failed
